Gate (Erc20 DAI Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard DAI "Dai")
Gate (Erc20 REP Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard REP "Augur")
Gate (Erc20 USDC Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard USDC "USD Coin" 6)

-- Now deploy our cTokens
Gate (XToken cZRX Address) (XToken Deploy XErc20 cZRX "Test 0x ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 ZRX Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (XToken cBAT Address) (XToken Deploy XErc20 cBAT "Test Basic Attention Token ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 BAT Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (XToken cDAI Address) (XToken Deploy XErc20 cDAI "Test Dai ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 DAI Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
